    </S>
    <S id="S2">
        <FORM>27 Karou ni-'ara tyn tana pi k'anna, ni-sa-ra rbou ta Littou ty-ni-æn. Annata ni-k'ma ta ti Jesus tyni-æn, Kamamang ka pam't-ei-mhou mei-dyss-â.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S3">
        <FORM>28 Ka assi mou mhga ki atta ta ti mamang neini-æn ka mie-roung hynna, alei kimang ka pa-sousou-en tyn [ta atta] tyni-æn.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S4">
        <FORM>20 Ka ni-pæhdimdim ta ra-rouma, alei ka mei-pauti ta ti Ju-das, ka pa-sousou-en ti Jesus tyni-æn, Peila-auto ki mǣ-iææpo-kyt-ta tou 'Ou-vavatoug-han, ka pi'æ-âl-ato lava ta teni ki-ma-mang ki malymmouk.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S5">
        <FORM>30 Irou ka ni-'ara tyn ta na pi k'anna ni-madys sa-mamala. Ka euvænnæn ta kidi.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S6">
        <FORM>31 Irou ka ni-sa-mamala ta te-ni, ni-k'ma ta ti Jesus, Pou-vavau-en-ato hnyn ki kidi ta Alak ki kæ-euloung, ka pou-vavau-in-nappa ki kidi ta Alid tyni-æn.</FORM>
    </S>
    <S id="S7">
        <FORM>32 Heirou ni-pou-vavau-in ki kidi ta Alid tyni-æn pouvavau-âl-appa ki kidi tyni-æn, ta Alid ty-ni-æn mamadou, ka pou-dis-ah pouvavau ki kidi tyni-æn.</FORM>
    </S>
